**Summary:** This documentation covers revenue tracking in Amplitude, including revenue properties ($revenue, $price, $quantity, $productId, $revenueType, $currency), configuration options for in-app purchases (IAPs) and non-in-app purchases, revenue verification using iTunes Connect Shared Secret or Google Play License Public Key, and the three revenue event types (Revenue, Revenue (Verified), Revenue (Unverified)) that appear in Revenue LTV charts.

